name: Heath-imager
tagline: Floppy Disk Imaging for Heathkit hard-sectored disks using Device Side's FC5025
body:
Floppy Disk Imaging for Heathkit hard-sectored disks using Device Side's FC5025.

With permission from Device Side, this program used parts of Device Side's source code for interfacing with the FC5025.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
